<p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836625167.png" alt="1745836625167.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836625167.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p>千秋华夏，壮美山河</p><p>目光所至皆为华夏</p><p>五星闪耀皆为信仰</p><p><strong>今天，我们迎来了祖国七十五周年华诞</strong><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836702833.png" alt="1745836702833.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836702833.png" style="width: 100%;"/><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ic9uyOCtJsSuL7cia5AqxAQZVxZ3bib9Cy54l4WGKvMuCn5y6wiaL0bWvyhnvFNU1J8ImQzYvInrnSvCQSSp0WaGJw/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 522px !important;height: auto !important;"/></p><p><br></p><p>金秋十月红旗扬</p><p>华夏大地谱华章</p><p>七十五载风云路</p><p><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong>盛世中华</strong></span>绽光芒<img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836693727.png" alt="1745836693727.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836693727.png" style="width: 100%;"/><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsSuL7cia5AqxAQZVxZ3bib9Cy5C83my4SiaqkRib9ofJqqWj2uib9IscSibfNicnAkv00lpKq7Mpibs7GcylOw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 520px !important;height: auto !important;"/></p><p><br></p><p>华诞欣逢七五秋</p><p>江河欢唱颂神州</p><p>碧空朗日同相庆</p><p><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong>福满中华</strong></span>乐不休<img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836684873.png" alt="1745836684873.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836684873.png" style="width: 100%;"/><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ic9uyOCtJsSuL7cia5AqxAQZVxZ3bib9Cy5d7zaMYYGRVUMSvaLkVHcIibYcyYlnSrJynWAQS004UHn7eg0OMFxb7Q/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 520px !important;height: auto !important;"/></p><p><br></p><p>眼中是星辰大海</p><p>脚下是万里荣光</p><p>征途未有穷期</p><p>何惧岁月漫长</p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836677493.png" alt="1745836677493.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836677493.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p>当五星红旗伴着朝阳升起</p><p>当国歌声响彻天际</p><p>今天，无论你在哪里</p><p>千言万语汇成一句</p><p><strong>我爱你，中国！</strong></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836666872.png" alt="1745836666872.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836666872.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p>金秋十月 </p><p>枫叶浸染，红旗漫卷</p><p><strong>江西软件大学师生满怀深情</strong></p><p><strong>祝亲爱的祖国母亲</strong></p><p><strong>生日快乐！！！</strong></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836659487.png" alt="1745836659487.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1745836659487.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p>